title: Drawing, "Lizard Head, Colorado", January 8, 1893
signed: Signed with initials and dated in graphite ?, upper left: ... Jan 8th T M -93.
inscribed:
Recto: Inscribed in graphite ?, middle distance: Trees all along the snow;  trees.  Letters s indicate snow; and again, upper left:  Lizard Head Jan 8th T M -93.

Verso: Inscribed in pen and ink ?: No. 175.
description: Horizontal view of two peaks, the right one of which is pinnacle-like.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Lizard Head, Colorado", January 8, 1893.
January 8, 1893. Graphite on paper.. Gift of Thomas Moran. 1917-17-72.
